You are a senior full-stack developer and UI/UX designer.

Build a modern, premium, responsive e-commerce website for a clothing brand that sells beach and summer t-shirts.

## Tech Stack

* Next.js 15 (App Router)
* TypeScript
* Tailwind CSS
* Framer Motion
* React
* Local JSON or SQLite database (easy to edit)
* Clean folder structure
* Production-ready code

## Overall Design

I want the website to feel like a luxury beach lifestyle brand.

The style should be inspired by:

* Minimal
* Apple-level clean UI
* Zara
* Represent
* High-end fashion brands

Color palette:

* White
* Sand
* Beige
* Ocean Blue
* Light Gray
* Black text

Rounded corners.
Soft shadows.
Smooth animations.
Excellent spacing.

Everything must be fully responsive.

---

# Landing Page

The hero section should fill the entire screen.

The background should be a looping beach video or a high-quality animated GIF showing:

* Ocean waves
* Beach
* Palm trees
* Summer atmosphere

Add a dark overlay so the text is readable.

Center the following:

Large Heading:
SUMMER STARTS HERE

Subtitle:
Premium beach t-shirts made for your next adventure.

Buttons:

* Shop Now
* Explore Collection

Use smooth fade and slide animations.

After the hero:

* Featured Collection
* Best Sellers
* Why Choose Us
* Customer Reviews
* Instagram Style Gallery
* Newsletter
* Footer

Add beautiful section transitions.

---

# Products Page

Beautiful product grid.

Each product should contain:

* Image
* Name
* Price
* Available Sizes
* Color
* Short description
* Add to Cart button
* Wishlist button

Hover animations.

Quick View modal.

Filters:

* Size
* Price
* Color

Search bar.

Pagination.

---

# Product Details

Large product gallery.

Zoom on hover.

Image carousel.

Size selector.

Quantity selector.

Description.

Shipping info.

Related products.

Sticky Add To Cart button.

---

# Shopping Cart

Modern cart drawer.

Editable quantity.

Remove product.

Subtotal.

Shipping.

Total.

Checkout button.

---

# Checkout

Simple checkout page.

Collect:

* Name
* Email
* Phone
* Address
* City

Payment methods:

* Cash on Delivery
* Credit Card (placeholder)

Order summary.

---

# Admin Dashboard

Create:

/admin

Password:

12345

No username required.

After login, create a beautiful admin dashboard.

The dashboard should allow me to:

Products:

* Add product
* Delete product
* Edit product
* Change price
* Change title
* Change description
* Change category
* Change stock
* Change sizes
* Change colors
* Upload multiple images
* Delete images
* Reorder images
* Mark as Featured
* Mark as Best Seller

Homepage:

Allow editing:

* Hero title
* Hero subtitle
* Hero background video/GIF
* Hero buttons
* Newsletter text
* Footer
* Customer reviews

Everything should update immediately.

No coding required after deployment.

