# Assets

Use placeholder products for now.

For the hero background, use one of these free resources:

Pexels:
https://www.pexels.com/videos/search/beach/

Pixabay:
https://pixabay.com/videos/search/beach/

Mixkit:
https://mixkit.co/free-stock-video/beach/

Coverr:
https://coverr.co/

The hero should automatically play the background video, be muted, loop forever, and work on desktop and mobile.

